      <title>北卡罗来纳州亚马逊工人申请工会选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-24/amazon-workers-in-north-carolina-file-for-union-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚马逊公司北卡罗来纳州仓库的员工向国家劳工关系委员会提交了一份请愿书，要求举行选举来确定该仓库的工人是否由工会代表。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-24/amazon-workers-in-north-carolina-file-for-union-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Dec 2024 00:44:40 GMT</pubDate>
